<item>
            <title>[PIG-4006] Make the interval of DAGStatus report configurable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4006</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, Pig prints DAGStatus for Tez jobs every second. This generates a lot of info message in stderr. In particular, for long running jobs, every second status report seems unnecessary.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1) Every 10 seconds seems reasonable for most jobs.&lt;br/&gt;
2) But if the default isn&apos;t good, users should be able to configure via a property.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
